-- This is a test control file

test_name 	 bad-bit-identifier-in-static
test_description A class has a call to a static feature `feature {FOO [BIT weasel]}.value' where FOO is an unconstrained generic class, but `weasel' is an unknown identifier.  The compiler accepts the class but should not.  Executing melting system prints "Error: could not read Eiffel update file".

copy_sub 	Ace $TEST Ace
copy_raw 	test.e $CLUSTER test.e
copy_raw 	test1.e $CLUSTER test1.e
compile_melted
compile_result 	validity_error TEST VEEN

test_end
